# No ARIA or role attributes

This codebase intentionally does not use ARIA or `role` attributes.

Do not add:
- `aria-*` attributes (e.g. `aria-label`, `aria-hidden`, `aria-live`, `aria-pressed`, `aria-expanded`, `aria-controls`)
- `role` attributes (e.g. `role="radiogroup"`, `role="button"`)

Use visible text, semantic HTML, and CSS for structure and presentation instead.
